{"data":[{"date":"10:40 06/08","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea chia s\u1ebb kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/hlv-sarri-tiet-lo-so-tan-binh-con-lai-cap-ben-chelsea-o-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi t\u00e2n HLV. Sau tr\u1eadn, Sarri chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ed1i lo l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nSarri c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng HLV \u0111\u1eb7t phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u00f4n ch\u1ec9, tuy nhi\u00ean Maurizio Sarri kh\u00f4ng t\u00e0i n\u00e0o l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Pep Guardiola gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n, v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 2 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 c\u00f9ng Man xanh. The Blues \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c 0-2, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Sergio Aguero.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, t\u00e2n HLV Sarri chia s\u1ebb \u00f4ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh n\u00e0y s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t bao nhi\u00eau th\u1eddi gian. T\u00f4i m\u1edbi t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 3 tu\u1ea7n, v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu 6 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong tay. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o t\u00f4i, v\u00e0o c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft n\u1eefa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea \" title=\"HLV Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/hlv-maurizio-sarri-du-am-tran-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu n\u1eefa v\u1edbi Lyon, v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, thay v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1y nh\u1ea3y tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u0169ng th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois, c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111ang th\u00f4ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u xin Chelsea cho m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n nghe tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1eeb mi\u1ec7ng c\u1ee7a Courtois, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda CLB n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c cao nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. Ngo\u00e0i ra, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn g\u00ec v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng tay c\u00f2&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Sarri chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/choi-mo-nhat-barkley-van-duoc-hlv-sarri-bao-ke-172-193816.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/choi-mo-nhat-barkley-van-duoc-hlv-sarri-bao-ke.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/choi-mo-nhat-barkley-van-duoc-hlv-sarri-bao-ke-172-193816.html\">Ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, Barkley v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri b\u1ea3o k\u00ea</span><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Barkley v\u00e0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chelsea trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-02-man-city-co-mot-napoli-phien-ban-loi-xuat-hien-172-193804.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/chelsea-02-man-city-co-mot-napoli-phien-ban-loi-xuat-hien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-02-man-city-co-mot-napoli-phien-ban-loi-xuat-hien-172-193804.html\">Chelsea 0-2 Man City: C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Napoli phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n l\u1ed7i xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n</span><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 mang theo tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf Napoli. Tuy nhi\u00ean, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Man City \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd t\u1ecf ra thua k\u00e9m h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n....</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-chelsea-02-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018-326-193798.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/video-tong-hop-chelsea-02-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-chelsea-02-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018-326-193798.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Chelsea 0-2 Man City (Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh 2018)</span><br>\r\nC\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Sergio Aguero \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Man City c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a HLV...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2053","checkdouble":"193831"},{"date":"09:59 06/08","title":"Real Madrid s\u1eafp bi\u1ebfn Harry Kane \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/real-madrid-sap-bien-harry-kane-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha hy v\u1ecdng Real Madrid s\u1ebd gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Modric c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Toni Kroos l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Los Blancos. Modric \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/19/Lucas-Vazquez-phat-bieu-ve-Luka-Modric-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t khi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Ronado \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, anh \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi Real t\u1edbi Juventus sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u00e0 Modric ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia. \u1ede n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, Tottenham, M.U v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i, \u1edf Italia, Inter Milan c\u0169ng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1985.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Modric, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ef1u sao Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nham-muc-tieu-200-trieu-euro-thay-modric-180-193772.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Eriksen</span> c\u1ee7a Tottenham n\u1ebfu Luka Modric ra \u0111i, Los Blancos c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra 200 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an\u00a0M\u1ea1ch. Ngo\u00e0i Eriksen th\u00ec Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus hay Ramsey c\u1ee7a Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Vazquez mu\u1ed1n Real gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Modric</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha hy v\u1ecdng Real Madrid s\u1ebd gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/vaz.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Vazquez mu\u1ed1n Real gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Modric th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, anh \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n anh \u1ea5y ra \u0111i v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i, Real kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Modric, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1edfi anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn. Song t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Modric \u1edf l\u1ea1i, anh \u1ea5y v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Real Madrid\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2052","checkdouble":"193833"},{"date":"10:12 06/08","title":"M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf Juventus \"kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp\" \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/muc-luong-cua-cristiano-ronaldo-o-juventus-khung-khiep-den-the-nao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo thu\u1ed9c h\u00e0ng top th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 so v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng chung \u1edf Serie A, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f2n th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 Juventus ch\u1ecbu ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Cr7.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus ch\u1ecbu ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ronaldo<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi ra 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo, Juventus t\u1eebng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 khi b\u1ecf ng\u1ea7n \u1ea5y ti\u1ec1n cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Juventus c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh ri\u00eang khi Ronaldo gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin gia t\u0103ng v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u1eb7t t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo toi Juventus\" title=\"Ronaldo toi Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/muc-luong-cua-cristiano-ronaldo-o-juventus-khung-khiep-den-the-nao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo g\u1ea5p h\u01a1n ba l\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee9ng sau t\u1ea1i Serie A.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, Juventus s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t m\u1ed7i n\u0103m 31 tri\u1ec7u euro ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho Ronaldo, con s\u1ed1 c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng chung c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 d\u01b0 d\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh. \u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ecbu ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Juventus, h\u00e3y so m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u1edbi Gonzalo Higuain, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i Serie A.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Higuain v\u1eeba r\u1eddi Juventus gia nh\u1eadp AC Milan v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Ronaldo. M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng Higuain nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i AC Milan cao th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 9 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1ed7i n\u0103m, ch\u01b0a b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n ba m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 cho Ronaldo m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt kh\u00e1c r\u1eb1ng Juventus c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Serie A. Trong top 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t Serie A hi\u1ec7n nay, Juventus chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u1ebfn 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Ronaldo (31 tri\u1ec7u euro), Paulo Dybala (7) v\u00e0 Douglas Costa (6). Hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf AC Milan l\u00e0 Higuain (9) v\u00e0 Donnarumma (6).&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Juventus c\u0169ng chi ra \u0111\u1ebfn 239.9 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u1ed3m Mattia Perin, Leonardo Bonucci, Joao Cancelo, Emre Can v\u00e0 Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Juventus h\u00e8 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-juventus-real-van-rat-dang-so-du-khong-co-ronaldo-180-193768.html\">HLV Juventus: Real v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-real-madrid-31-juventus-icc-2018-329-193746.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Real Madrid 3-1 Juventus (ICC 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/leonardo-bonucci-khong-xin-loi-sau-khi-tro-lai-juventus-176-193737.html\">Leonardo Bonucci quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng xin l\u1ed7i sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-juventus-tran-dau-icc-2018-372-193731.html\">Real Madrid 3-1 Juventus (KT): Los Blancos t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Lopetegui ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t g\u1ecdn B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-tai-hop-cuu-den-juventus-kho-lam-nen-chuyen-o-champions-league-176-193654.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: T\u00e1i h\u1ee3p &ldquo;c\u1eebu \u0111en&rdquo;, Juventus kh\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf Champions League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tan-man/tom-cruise-cristiano-ronaldo-tuoi-tac-co-gi-ma-bat-kha-thi-392-192631.html\">Tom Cruise - Cristiano Ronaldo: Tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c c\u00f3 g\u00ec m\u00e0 b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2051","checkdouble":"193834"},{"date":"10:18 06/08","title":"Aaron Ramsey ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn v\u00f2i v\u0129nh Arsenal b\u1eb1ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/6/aaron-ramsey-phu-nhan-voi-vinh-arsenal-bang-luong-khung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Sun \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Song ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ramsey \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aaron Ramsey v\u1edbi Arsenal ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990. Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Arsenal, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/Thuc-hu-chuyen-Aaron-Ramsey-roi-Arsenal-neu-khong-co-luong-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ramsey \u0111\u00f2i m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRamsey x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu Arsenal t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i nh\u1eefng mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Ramsey \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, anh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb The Sun, Ramsey y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Vi\u1ec7c Arsenal \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 350.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n cho Mesut Ozil l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u00f2i l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo The Sun, Ramsey \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c bu\u1ed9c Arsenal ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea, M.U v\u00e0 Man City.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua, Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chi-40-trieu-bang-chelsea-quyet-tam-mua-bang-duoc-sao-khung-arsenal-172-193778.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ramsey</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00c1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn Arsenal g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng cho Ramsey ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ramsey ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn v\u00f2i v\u0129nh Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Sun \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Song ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/Truoc-tuong-lai-bat-dinh,-Aaron-Ramsey-phat-bieu-ve-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ramsey ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2i l\u01b0\u01a1ng 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf b\u1ea3n giao k\u00e8o m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u01a1 quan \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ramsey kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo ngu\u1ed3n tin \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb Goal, m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Ramsey y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u00e0 Arsenal ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal t\u1eeb Cardiff, Ramsey \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 327 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ghi 58 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Anh l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Arsenal d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Arsene Wenger, t\u00e2n HLV Emery c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2050","checkdouble":"193837"},{"date":"10:39 06/08","title":"Lucas Vazquez mu\u1ed1n Real gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/vaz.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha hy v\u1ecdng Real Madrid s\u1ebd gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Modric c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Toni Kroos l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Los Blancos. Modric \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/19/Lucas-Vazquez-phat-bieu-ve-Luka-Modric-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t khi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Ronado \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, anh \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi Real t\u1edbi Juventus sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u00e0 Modric ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia. \u1ede n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, Tottenham, M.U v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i, \u1edf Italia, Inter Milan c\u0169ng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1985.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Modric, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ef1u sao Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nham-muc-tieu-200-trieu-euro-thay-modric-180-193772.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Eriksen</span> c\u1ee7a Tottenham n\u1ebfu Luka Modric ra \u0111i, Los Blancos c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra 200 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an\u00a0M\u1ea1ch. Ngo\u00e0i Eriksen th\u00ec Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus hay Ramsey c\u1ee7a Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Vazquez mu\u1ed1n Real gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Modric</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha hy v\u1ecdng Real Madrid s\u1ebd gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/vaz.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Vazquez mu\u1ed1n Real gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Modric th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, anh \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n anh \u1ea5y ra \u0111i v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i, Real kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Modric, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1edfi anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn. Song t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Modric \u1edf l\u1ea1i, anh \u1ea5y v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Real Madrid\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2049","checkdouble":"193838"},{"date":"10:09 06/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Hull vs Aston Villa 01h45 ng\u00e0y 7/8 (H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/nhan-dinh-hull-vs-aston-villa-01h45-ngay-78-hang-nhat-anh-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay Hull vs Aston Villa l\u00fac 01h45 ng\u00e0y 7/8 (V\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh Championship 2018/19): \u00dd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Hull vs Aston Villa 1h45 ng\u00e0y 78 H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Hull vs Aston Villa 1h45 ng\u00e0y 78 H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Hull-City-vs-Aston-Villa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hull vs Aston Villa</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Hull vs Aston Villa: 0-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, Hull City ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh sau khi t\u1ee5t h\u1ea1ng t\u1eeb Premier League. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, The Tigers thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 khi ch\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 18/24 \u0111\u1ed9i. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Aston Villa \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft play-off th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng Premier League nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 thua Fulham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Hull \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 6 t\u00e2n binh tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00edt t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t chia tay nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Dawson, Abel Hernandez, Allan McGregor, David Meyler hay Sebastian Larsson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Hull City kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1t khi sau 7 m\u00e0n t\u1eadp d\u01b0\u1ee3t, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nigel Adkins ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng (thua 2) d\u00f9 to\u00e0n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh. V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Championship m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/18, tuy c\u00f3 \u01b0u th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Hull City c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp ngang c\u01a1 Aston Villa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Aston Villa, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 chi\u00eau m\u00f4 1 t\u00e2n binh l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Moreira (Atletico Madrid). Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng, The Villa \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng. Nh\u1edd gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, Aston Villa \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi khi lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf 4/5 tr\u1eadn. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 - ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Steve Bruce, The Villa c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay. 12 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Hull tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Villa Park m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 thua duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n so t\u00e0i gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00eam nay kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 Hull v\u00e0 Aston Villa \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Aston Villa ch\u1ec9 thua 1/12 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Hull City tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y (th\u1eafng 8, h\u00f2a 3, thua 1).<br>\r\n- 3 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n- Aston Villa kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng trong 3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Hull (h\u00f2a 2, thua 1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\n- Hull City: \u0110\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n- Aston Villa: V\u1eafng Ritchie de Laet (treo gi\u00f2); Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Keinan Davis, Scott Hogan v\u00e0 Rushian Hepburn-Murphy c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2048","checkdouble":"193839"},{"date":"10:15 06/08","title":"Gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh, Pep s\u00e1nh ngang\u2026 \u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn\u201d David Moyes","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/gianh-sieu-cup-anh-pep-sanh-ngang-nguoi-duoc-chon-david-moyes.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin v\u1edb v\u1ea9n, Pep Guardiola s\u00e1nh ngang David Moyes sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Community Shield m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nPep c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi Moyes<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh khai h\u1ed9i 1 tu\u1ea7n, tr\u1eadn tranh Community Shield s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra gi\u1eefa nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Premier League v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 FA Cup. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Man City \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Chelsea v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c 2-0, Kun Aguero l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Pep Guardiola c\u00f9ng Man City \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u1edbi Man United m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2013-14, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m &ldquo;Sir&rdquo; David Moyes v\u1eabn c\u00f2n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, M.U n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ea3 Premier League l\u1eabn Community Shield trong m\u1ed9t n\u0103m, v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t Man City c\u1ee7a Pep v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, M.U v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2012-13 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sir Alex Ferguson, v\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh m\u00e0 h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a David Moyes. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap FA.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gi\u00e0nh si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh, HLV Pep Guardiola s\u00e1nh ngang David Moyes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gi\u00e0nh si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh, HLV Pep Guardiola s\u00e1nh ngang David Moyes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/pep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola s\u00e1nh ngang David Moyes</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u0103m \u0111\u00f3, M.U c\u1ee7a Moyes \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Wigan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0, Van Persie l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap. 1 n\u0103m sau, \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap FA l\u00e0 Arsenal h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0110KV\u0110 Premier League Man City v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0. Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh c\u00fap FA (Arsenal, Man United, Arsenal) \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh Premier League (Chelsea, Leicester, Chelsea). \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng, nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EPL m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 b\u1ecf c\u00e1i d\u1edbp n\u00e0y, khi h\u1ecd h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Chelsea (v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA) v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh CLB \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2013 gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea3 EPL l\u1eabn Community Shield trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Pep Guardiola s\u00e1nh ngang David Moyes.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2010 (Man United) v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League khi gi\u00e0nh si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh ti\u1ec1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed 2 \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Arsenal v\u00e0 Man United, \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i d\u1edbp tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Man City.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u1eefng CLB gi\u00e0nh si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i<br>\r\n</strong> <br>\r\n<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"106%\" style=\"width:106.54%;background:#FFFFCC;border-collapse:collapse;border:none;&#10; mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:&#10; 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"12%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:12.08%;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;&#10;  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\">\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><b>N\u0103m</b></span></span><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"18%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:18.18%;border:solid windowtext 1