ua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a HLV...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2047","checkdouble":"193840"},{"date":"11:39 06/08","title":"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 6/8: M.U \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Boateng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/ngay-hom-nay-68.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (6/8). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2>(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)<br>\r\n<h2>M.U \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Boateng</h2>\r\nR\u1ea5t nhanh v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, MU \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng t\u1eeb Bayern Munich. T\u1edd Bild \u0111\u01b0a tin, tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u00e0 MU thua Bayern Munich 0-1 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Boateng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMU xem Boateng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, sau khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Bonucci, Maguire hay Mina. Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 t\u1ea1i Premier League s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda (kh\u00f4ng mua, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p b\u00e1n), v\u00e0 MU c\u0169ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp Leicester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf n\u00ean, cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Bayern Munich \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhanh. Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1ee7a Bild, MU s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00e1c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Boateng trong 1-2 ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 68, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 68, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/boateng-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri ra t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu th\u01b0 cho Courtois</h2>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ra t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu th\u01b0 cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a CLB Real Madrid. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 26 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea. G\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Courtois l\u00e0 Christophe Henrotay ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng CLB Chelsea n\u00ean b\u00e1n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 cho Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3 v\u00ec t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Courtois. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n nghe tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Courtois n\u00f3i. N\u1ebfu Courtois n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi CLB, b\u1edfi v\u00ec t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t\u201d, HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-dai-dien-cau-xin-chelsea-hay-buong-tha-cho-courtois-172-193720.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u xin Chelsea h\u00e3y bu\u00f4ng tha cho Courtois</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Marcelo</h2>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Corriere della Sera (Italy), Juventus v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Marcelo trong m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Marcelo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus sau khi Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Juventus l\u00e0 Alex Sandro \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 gia nh\u1eadp PSG. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i, Juventus s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Marcelo. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Paul Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Miralem Pjanic ra \u0111i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c CLB nh\u01b0 PSG, Chelsea v\u00e0 Barcelona.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/pogba-marcelo-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham r\u00fat lui, Chelsea r\u1ed9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n Zaha</h2>\r\nTheo t\u1edd The Sun, Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Wilfried Zaha c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace. Palace \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 h\u00e9t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u00ean t\u1edbi t\u1eadn 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Zaha v\u00e0 Tottenham nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ea3. Hi\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Chelsea c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m cho c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a MU.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-hang-thai-mu-len-75-trieu-bang-172-193773.html\">Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua \u201ch\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d MU l\u00ean 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n Gundogan</h2>\r\nT\u1edd Tuttosport t\u1ea1i Italia cho bi\u1ebft Inter Milan \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecfi mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 illkay Gundogan c\u1ee7a Man City. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t Arturo Vidal v\u00e0o tay Barcelona c\u00f2n Luka Modric l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, Inter hy v\u1ecdng Gundogan s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. Gundogan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Pep Guardiola tin d\u00f9ng nh\u01b0ng anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man City.\r\n<h2>HLV Valverde hy v\u1ecdng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Cillessen</h2>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb Jasper Cillessen \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y khi m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t CLB Premier League mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecfi mua anh, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf Barcelona sau Marc-Andre Ter Stegen. HLV Ernesto Valverde cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi CLB, n\u00f3i: \u201c\u00dd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u00f3 2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Jasper v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y\u201d.\r\n<h2>Giroud kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed3n Marseille mu\u1ed1n m\u1eddi Olivier Giroud tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p thi \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Chelsea ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y. \u201cL\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p thi \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb, c\u00f2n kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 \u1edf c\u1ea5p CLB v\u00e0 \u0110TQG\u201d, Giroud n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2046","checkdouble":"193842"},{"date":"11:58 06/08","title":"Rashford v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i: Tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/6/rashford-va-chiec-ao-huyen-thoai-trach-nhiem-nang-ne-kha-nang-han-che.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi (thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bayern), M.U \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00e1 l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm \u2013 Marcus Rasford nh\u1eadn chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMourinho kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ai \u0111\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ee7. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Wayne Rooney chia tay Man United \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Everton, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t Zlatan Ibrahimovic m\u1eb7c n\u00f3 trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Man United. Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng cho Ibra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng, v\u00e0 anh n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi MLS thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 n\u00e0o tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mourinho-ti-nanh-voi-cac-doi-thu-khong-ngung-voi-vinh-bld-man-utd-172-193823.html\" target=\"_blank\">Jose Mourinho ch\u1eedi h\u1ebft h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ebfn\u2026 Ed Woodward</span>. Tuy nhi\u00ean khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh c\u00f3, v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>V\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 trao chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 cho Marcus Rashford!<br>\r\n</strong> <br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rasford nh\u1eadn chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Rasford nh\u1eadn chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 T\u00e0i n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng g\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Rasford-nhan-chiec-ao-so-10-Tai-nang-khong-ganh-duoc-trach-nhiem-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marcus Rashford s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00e2n s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a s\u00e2n Old Trafford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u00edch n\u00f3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n khao kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o n\u00e0y. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Marcus c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Wayne Rooney, v\u00e0 sau n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Zlatan Ibrahimovic. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n n\u00fap b\u00f3ng, ch\u1edd th\u1eddi c\u01a1 v\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y, CLB \u0111\u00e3 trao cho Marcus.<strong> D\u00f9 sao n\u00f3 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0!\u201d</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hay n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, Mourinho kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 trao chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 \u2013 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i gi\u1edd b\u1ecb b\u1ecf tr\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ai \u201cth\u00e8m\u201d m\u1eb7c. M\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 xu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea5p l\u1edbn v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ee1 ng\u00e0ng v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Marcus Rashford ra qu\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn thua Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 ra nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. \u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t mang t\u00ednh bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 Denis Law, Mark Hughes, David Beckham (tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec3n sang s\u1ed1 7), Teddy Sheringham, Van Nistelrooy v\u00e0 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u1edbi k\u1ec3 \u1edf tr\u00ean. \u0110\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Marcus Rashford, ch\u00e0ng trai tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh t\u00edch chung c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 anh l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Liverpool 2-1, v\u00e0 h\u1ebft. Sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd v\u1eabn \u0111ang v\u1eadt l\u1ed9n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Nh\u00e0 h\u00e1t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1.\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rashford v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Rashford v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Rashford-va-chiec-ao-huyen-thoai-Trach-nhiem-nang-ne,-kha-nang-han-che-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho: \"C\u1eadu ta th\u00edch \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4i, n\u00f3 c\u00f2n tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0!\"</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>\u00a0</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Khi s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111i k\u00e8m \u00e1p l\u1ef1c<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"With great power comes great responsibility\u201d <strong>(N\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u00e0ng l\u1edbn, tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u00e0ng cao) </strong>\u2013 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e2u n\u00f3i m\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng nghe qua, trong b\u1ed9 phim Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i t\u1eed Tobey Maguire. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00e0ng trai Peter Parker l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t si\u00eau anh h\u00f9ng b\u1ecb bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed5i gen sau khi b\u1ecb nh\u1ec7n c\u1eafn, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khuy\u00ean nh\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1ed1ng c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Peter l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc sinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng, nghe kh\u00e1 li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh \u201cb\u01a1m v\u00e1\u201d v\u1ec1 Marcus Rashford. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n trao cho t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb m\u1ed9t \u201c<strong>b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp l\u00e0m si\u00eau anh h\u00f9ng\u201d</strong>, b\u1edfi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, Rashford v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt v\u1edbi phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rasford nh\u1eadn chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Rashford 10\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/rah.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rashford kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng thay th\u1ebf Wayne Rooney</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRashford v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, khi\u1ebfn anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb Kylian Mbappe c\u1ee7a PSG. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7, Rashford kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng suy ngh\u0129 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00e1 \u201ct\u0103m t\u1ed1i\u201d. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u2013 hay n\u00f4m na l\u00e0 \u201cngu d\u1ed1t\u201d.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn thua Bayern Munich m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. V\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Rashford l\u00e0 pha \u0111\u1ee1 h\u1ee5t b\u00f3ng khi b\u1eadt l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Javi Martinez \u0111\u1ee9ng y\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean m\u1ed7i th\u1eddi m\u1ed7i kh\u00e1c, c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng ai \u201cn\u1ee1\u201d so s\u00e1nh m\u1ed9t c\u1eadu b\u00e9 ch\u01b0a b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 20 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra. Nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3i v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra, Rashford kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e0n anh Rooney.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rasford nh\u1eadn chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Rashford vs Bayern\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/rash.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rashford nh\u1eadn chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bayern</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 th\u1eeba s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin, nh\u01b0ng g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, vi\u1ec7c trao chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 cho sao tr\u1ebb tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u2013 m\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn. M\u1ed7i khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7, s\u1ef1 so s\u00e1nh s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n b\u1edfi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng l\u1eafm m\u1ed3m c\u1ee7a x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u00e2m lao ph\u1ea3i theo lao. L\u00fac n\u00e0y Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch hy v\u1ecdng <span href=\"http://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-man-utd-chinh-thuc-tim-ra-tan-chu-nhan-cho-ao-so-10-172-193824.html\" target=\"_blank\">Marcus Rasford nh\u1eadn chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10</span> v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc, x\u00f3a tan ho\u00e0i nghi v\u00e0 d\u1eb9p b\u1ecf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh \u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/de-gianh-chien-thang-mourinho-duoc-yeu-cau-lam-dieu-bat-ngo-172-193670.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/de-gianh-chien-thang-mourinho-duoc-yeu-cau-lam-dieu-bat-ngo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/de-gianh-chien-thang-mourinho-duoc-yeu-cau-lam-dieu-bat-ngo-172-193670.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd</span><br>\r\nSau nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, theo c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Man United \u2013 Brian McClair.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-bayern-munich-10-mu-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-329-193818.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/video-tong-hop-bayern-munich-10-mu-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-bayern-munich-10-mu-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-329-193818.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Bayern Munich 1-0 MU (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadp d\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 t\u00e2m l\u00fd s\u1ee3 thua khi ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/bayern-munich-vs-mu-tran-dau-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-372-193792.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/bayern-munich-vs-mu-tran-dau-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/bayern-munich-vs-mu-tran-dau-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-372-193792.html\">Bayern Munich 1-0 MU: \u0110\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e1 th\u1eadt, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf thua ... c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadp d\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 t\u00e2m l\u00fd s\u1ee3 thua khi ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2045","checkdouble":"193843"},{"date":"07:48 06/08","title":"H\u00e0ng hot World Cup ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \"th\u1ea3 th\u00ednh\" Man Utd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/hang-hot-world-cup-tiep-tuc-tha-thinh-man-utd.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Rakitic ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng Premier League khi th\u1eddi gian ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 29.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p s\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn b\u1edfi Ivan Rakitic, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 chung k\u1ebft. Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh 29 tu\u1ed5i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Man Utd th\u00e8m mu\u1ed1n anh, sau n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1edfi th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc v\u1edbi Inter Milan.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Perisic c\u1ee7a Inter Milan \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Perisic c\u1ee7a Inter Milan \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/hang-hot-world-cup-tiep-tuc-tha-thinh-man-utd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Perisic c\u1ee7a Inter Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, Perisic l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t &ldquo;th\u1ea3 th\u00ednh&rdquo; c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 n\u1ed9i dung mu\u1ed1n chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Croatia: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao n\u1eefa. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1eed s\u1ee9c \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn kh\u00e1c, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng n\u1eafm b\u1eaft cho b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia nh\u1eadp Premier League n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh hay La Liga c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o mong mu\u1ed1n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u v\u00e0 l\u00e0m g\u00ec r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea5y.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda t\u1ea1i Anh v\u00e0o h\u1ebft ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 n\u0103m 9/8 trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u cho Man Utd h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t trong ba c\u00e1i t\u00ean Toby Alderweireld, Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Yerry Mina c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford v\u00e0o gi\u1edd ch\u00f3t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tien-ve-ivan-perisic-dat-xat-ra-mieng-cho-mu-172-164447.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/21/tin-nong-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-247-inter-milan-san-sang-ban-ivan-perisic-cho-mu-neu-.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tien-ve-ivan-perisic-dat-xat-ra-mieng-cho-mu-172-164447.html\">Ivan Perisic: \u0110\u1eaft x\u1eaft ra mi\u1ebfng cho Man Utd</span><br>\r\n48 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 28 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a ph\u00fat gi\u00e2y n\u00e0o th\u1eed l\u1eeda \u1edf Premier League, \u0111\u00f3 hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t canh b\u1ea1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia &ndash;...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2044","checkdouble":"193822"},{"date":"07:12 06/08","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (6/8/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-682018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 6/8 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u00f4ng tin ng\u00e0y gi\u1edd c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00eam/r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/lich.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: cen